T02D1212:313b-3: dur khrod brgyad ces bya ba /
T02D1212:313b-4: kye'i rdo rje la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D1212:313b-5: zhing brgyad la sogs pa rnams 'jig rten skyong ba brgyad po dang /
T02D1212:313b-6: klu'i rgyal po rigs brgyad dang /
T02D1212:313b-7: zhing gi bdag po'i lha dang /
T02D1212:313b-9: char sprin rim pa ji lta ba bzhin blta bar bya'o //
T02D1212:313b-10: dang por re zhig shar du n'a ga pushpa'i shing dang /
T02D1212:313b-13: klu'i rgyal po padma chen po dang /
T02D1212:313b-14: char sprin gho ra zhes bya ba gur gum gyi mdog lta bu'o //
T02D1212:313b-15: lho ru aa mra'i shing dang /
T02D1212:313b-18: klu'i rgyal po rigs ldan dang /
T02D1212:313b-19: char sprin tsanda zhes bya ba sngon po'o //
T02D1212:313b-20: nub tu shing aa shvattha dang /
T02D1212:313b-23: klu'i rgyal po stobs kyi rgyu dang /
T02D1212:313b-24: char sprin gha na zhes bya ba mdog dkar po'o //
T02D1212:313b-25: byang du shing punn'a ga ra dang /
T02D1212:313b-28: klu'i rgyal po dung skyong dang /
T02D1212:313b-29: char sprin aa pa rto zhes bya ba kha dog ser po'o //
T02D1212:313b-30: dbang ldan du shing n+ya gro dha dang /
T02D1212:313b-34: char sprin gardzi ta zhes bya ba kha dog nag po'o //
T02D1212:313b-35: me ru shing ka ranydza dang /
T02D1212:313b-38: klu'i rgyal po padma zhes bya ba dang /
T02D1212:313b-39: char sprin gharmi ta zhes bya ba kha dog sna tshogs so //
T02D1212:313b-40: bden pral du la ta dza ta'i shing dang /
T02D1212:313b-43: klu'i rgyal po mtha' yas dang /
T02D1212:313b-44: char sprin 'bab pa zhes bya ba nag po'o //
T02D1212:313b-45: rlung du shing au dumw'a ra dang /
T02D1212:314a-2: / klu'i rgyal po nor rgyas kyi bu dang /
T02D1212:314a-3: char sprin pu r'a na zhes bya ba dkar nag
T02D1212:314a-4: gi mdog go zhes bya ba la sogs pa'i zhing
T02D1212:314a-5: rim pa ji lta bas shes par bya'o /
T02D1212:314a-7: // / rgya gar gyi mkhan po ratna shr'i mi tra dang /
